<br />&amp;amp;quot;proficient to expert level of ability in the MS Office suite&amp;amp;quot;
<br /><br />As you can see, there is emphasis on the MS Office programs, scheduling, and presentations. So you MUST include those words in your Michigan Unemployment.
<br /><br />3. Always include a cover letter detailing the exact position you are interested in, where you saw the job listing, and why you are interested, not just that you are interested.
<br /><br />Doing this will automatically make you stand apart from everyone else and will make it clear to the hiring manager what you have to offer and what you are seeking.
